    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织对澳大利亚养老基金的私人资产风险发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/imf-warns-on-australian-pension-funds-private-assets-exposure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织 (International Monetary Fund) 的分析显示，澳大利亚快速增长的养老金行业规模达 3.9 万亿澳元（2.6 万亿美元），由于私人市场投资的增加，导致市场出现大幅波动的可能性更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/imf-warns-on-australian-pension-funds-private-assets-exposure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 23:21:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地缘政治因素促使交易商转向避险，黄金价格接近历史最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-geopolitics-drive-traders-to-safety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金稳定在历史高位附近，因为投资者关注即将到来的美国大选和中东冲突，黄金获得持续的避险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-geopolitics-drive-traders-to-safety</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 23:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高监管机构呼吁关注私人信贷的估值风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/top-regulators-call-out-valuation-risks-in-private-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球各大金融监管机构都对私人信贷估值、贷方是否隐藏问题贷款以及私人市场和保险资金之间的深度纠葛表示担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/top-regulators-call-out-valuation-risks-in-private-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 22:35:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球抛售后美国国债持跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券市场持续下跌，美国股市表现挣扎，因交易员们担心美联储降息步伐放缓。亚洲股市开盘涨跌互现。]]></description>
